Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:36.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:44.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:49.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:54.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:59.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:09.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:20.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:30.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:37.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:43.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:50.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:36.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.08,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:44.21,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光暈  浮現於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:49.42,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,未見未知的陽光  會將誰照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:54.18,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,我親愛的伙伴  就算沉浸於悲傷也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:59.14,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.43,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  來伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.81,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿過這片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.02,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  衝擊全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:09.65,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.32,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,緊盯著世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:20.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,當小小胸膛填滿了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:30.09,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,琥珀之夢  朝著約定的地點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:37.47,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,對你的關心關愛  比這天空更寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:43.60,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,無限擴張  永無止境
Comment: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:50.53,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.40,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:16.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}住み慣れたこの街を出てゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:19.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}新しい世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}まだ見ぬ色を　探しに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:24.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I can not do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:30.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}素直になれないこともあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:33.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}あの虹の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:36.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}行ってみたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:44.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}頭に浮かんだイメージを抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:50.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I will never ever give up halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:58.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}どこまでも　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:05.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I wanna make my life shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:16.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}輝くよ　あの虹の向こうまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.89,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想要出發
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:16.02,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}離開這熟悉的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:19.19,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}去探索新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.11,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}尋找從未見過的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:24.57,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:30.54,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}有時也會不夠坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:33.67,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}那彩虹的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:36.50,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想試著去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:44.13,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}記住浮現在頭腦中的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:50.97,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我永遠不會半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:58.57,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不論到哪裡  不論走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:05.57,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想讓自己的生命更閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:16.50,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}釋放光芒吧  直到那彩虹的彼端
